---
description: Standards for working with environment variables
globs: "**/*.py"
alwaysApply: false
---
- Use os.environ.get() with default values for environment variables
- Prefix PDD-specific environment variables with "PDD_"
- Document environment variables in README.md
- For API keys, check for environment variables using consistent patterns
- Support both explicit configuration and fallback to environment variables
- When adding new environment variables, update .env.example
